               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> (v. <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጽእሞ፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምጽአሞ፡</foreign>, etiam per <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዐ</foreign>) <gramGrp> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos> </gramGrp> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> sonus repercussus </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> vox reciproca </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> echo </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> locus vocibus resonans </t:quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ይመልእ፡ ውስተ፡ አብያቲሃ፡ መጽአሞ፡</foreign> (c. varr.) <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἤχου</foreign> <ref cRef="Jes." loc="13,21">Jes. 13,21</ref> (ubi in glossa quadam marginali male explicatur <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘንዶ፡</foreign>); <ref cRef="Job" loc="4,13">Job 4,13</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ይዌውዑ፡ ማእከለ፡ መጽአሞ፡</foreign> (v. <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምጽዓሞ፡</foreign>) <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἀνὰ μέσον εὐήχων</foreign> <ref cRef="Job" loc="30,7">Job 30,7</ref>. – <lbl expand="">Sec.</lbl> Lud. „de <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> spectris </t:quote></cit> vel <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> phantasmatibus </t:quote></cit> quae circa moribundos vel visa vel metu credita sunt, accipitur“; <ref cRef="Org." loc="3 ">Org. 3 </ref>– <lbl expand="Vocabularium Aethiopicum, -a -a">Voc. Ae.</lbl>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጼዴንያት፡ ወመጽአሞ፡ ዘ፡ መልአከ፡ ሞት፡</foreign> </sense>
               
